{"tid":1572844,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"三毛分化撚屌FA","createTime":"2019-09-15T19:08:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T20:37:15.000Z","uid":211021,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d240e81bc7d486d5f4e220210635e96be86c98c8","tid":1572844,"uid":211021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T19:08:51.000Z","msg":"我係一個三毛口中嘅垃圾FA，我只係一個係地口中所講嘅垃圾救藍絲嘅傻鳩<br />\n<br />\n我知道大家俾班藍絲打係好嬲，我亦都唔會介入你地嘅衝突現場去方隔雙方，我無意去咁做，亦都冇咁嘅本事俾人拎刀斬<br />\n<br />\n但唔該，我從來冇唔救過任何一個傷者，就算你地俾刀斬都好，我地一定會救，因為我地做緊嘅係人道救援，唔係偏私淨救其中一邊。今時今日有幾多個FA俾人拉過，你地班三毛又知唔知？1 team FA有4-5人好正常，大家有時學嘅野係唔同，分工救人點都好過單機啦，乜野叫爭住救？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf6400948e38ae46cc5549a4614ab66854d381e7","tid":1572844,"uid":276916,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T19:11:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d890c3e6b37f00349c4dc6148948ebb1274a41ba","tid":1572844,"uid":211021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T19:12:00.000Z","msg":"見唔見到粒布袋彈，咩叫拎光環啊三毛狗，你覺得我地唔會俾人瞄住打？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0sgAMD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0sgAMD.jpg&h=e54210b9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b79edeee5303c43684965c7606b3d94a9509b002","tid":1572844,"uid":211021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T19:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZH69bkJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZH69bkJ.jpg&h=5c461474&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t3t30d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft3t30d5.jpg&h=2e5b9178&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11f1f05dbbbecc0ac1dc205c567136b43a8e6bb6","tid":1572844,"uid":211021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"cf6400948e38ae46cc5549a4614ab66854d381e7","tid":1572844,"uid":276916,"like":0,"dislike":13,"score":-13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T19:11:01.000Z","msg"